data.description: BOM due to buyer unable to obtain financing! Yes, you can have it all...a fresh, spacious and move-in ready home! And...qualifying applicants can assume the seller's 2.75% interest rate FHA loan! A rocking chair front porch greets you and your guests as you enter the home. Inside, the foyer gives way to a wonderful flex space that can be used as a play room, education center or is large enough to split into formal living and formal dining. This dapper dwelling is versatile…it can be someone’s future homestead, their winter retreat OR a lucrative addition to an investor’s portfolio. Walking through the home, you'll find that it has been meticulously taken care of.  Many of the major systems have either been well maintained or recently replaced...including a new roof in Sept 2023! Positioned ideally, in a gated community and on impressive interior lot, the possibilities are endless with the potential to add a private pool or additional storage! Speaking of the oversized yard, you'll find that the tall shady oak trees and quiet street are the perfect location for a peaceful retreat. Centrally located in the charming Bloomingdale Trails neighborhood, you’ll be minutes to everywhere you want to be…I-75, Brandon Mall, Downtown Tampa and more! Walking the neighborhood, you’ll be greeted by friendly neighbors' waves & salutations! If you are ready to find your piece of Florida, come see why this is a one-of-a-kind place to call home!
